collectible.name: Feathered Fury
collectible.description: "I own this sidewalk, and I'll take my sweet time crossing, thank you very much." Meet Feathered Fury, a connoisseur of al fresco dining, specializing in finding the most exotic leftovers from yesterday's lunch. Its plumage is not just gray; it's a mosaic of shimmering voxels, with each pixel a testament to its undeniable presence in the digital airspace. The latest in urban camouflage fashion, it's designed to blend seamlessly with the color palette of that overflowing dumpster.
